     6→/**
     7→ * This hook is necessary to prevent buggy behavior on iOS devices (need to test on Android).
     8→ * I won't get into too much detail about what bugs it solves, but so far I've found that setting the body to `position: fixed` is the most reliable way to prevent those bugs.
     9→ * Issues that this hook solves:
    10→ * https://github.com/emilkowalski/vaul/issues/435
    11→ * https://github.com/emilkowalski/vaul/issues/433
    12→ * And more that I discovered, but were just not reported.
    13→ */
